Given an array Arr of N positive integers, find K largest elements from the array.  The output elements should be printed in decreasing order.

class Solution {
    int[] kLargest(int[] arr, int n, int k) {
        // code here
        Arrays.sort(arr);
        int a[]= new int[k];
        for(int i=0;i<k;i++){
            a[i]=arr[n-i-1];
            
        }
        return a;
    }
}
